parcel.name: West End NFT Shopping Center
parcel.description: Come on down to the West End Shopping Center! Looking for a bite to eat? Pick up a wearable burger at Crypto Burger! Stop by Rev's Pet Block if your looking for some fuzzy NTF's. More on the techy side? Check out the Urbit ID shop for the future of operating systems. Pick up a chocolate bar at the Crypto Snack shack or swing by the Mouser Apparell store for some sweet wearables! More shops on the way with so keep checking in!

features.text:
# Crypto Burger

Grab a limited edition wearable Crypto Burger! Limited to 30 Original Burgers.

# Just .01 ETH!

--- Click the menu to buy!

# URBIT

Urbit OS is a clean slate reimagining of the operating system as an 'overlay OS.' It runs on any Unix machine with an internet connection.

It's a compact system for an individual to run their own permanent personal server.

Urbit ID is a decentralized digital identity system. Your Urbit ID is a username, network address, and crypto wallet.

Both are designed to work together as a single system

#"HAPPY PIXELS"
##PixelChain Artwork by Reviiser
###Edition 1 of 1

Portrait of the legendary Bob Ross forever immortalized on the blockchain with the PixelChain Dapp.

Pixelchain is a decentralized app that allows users to create 32x32 pixel art and store it 100% on the blockchain, where it will live forever. Every piece of artwork is unique and encoded into an ERC-721 token.

# Urbit OS

Urbit is a clean-slate OS and network for the 21st century.
